com.att.aro.pcap.packetRebuild

Class PCapPacketHeader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.aro.pcap.packetRebuild.PCapPacketHeader

  • public class PCapPacketHeader
extends java.lang.Object
    Pkt header in the libcap file. struct sf_pkthdr { struct timeval ts; UINT caplen; UINT len; }; The caplen is the portion of the packet found in the cap (it's possible that only part of the packet will be recorded). The len is the packet len as recorded.
    Author:
    roni bar-yanai
